CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1774365082
OL,3,CMan who drank six pints before fatal
OL,4,Ccrash that killed friend, jailed
OL,6,FA man has been jailed after his
OL,7,Fdangerous driving killed his friend in
OL,8,Fa crash, while under the influence of
OL,9,Falcohol.
OL,11,FMatthew Bennett, 23 lost control of
OL,12,Fhis car and collided two sets of trees
OL,13,Fon Friday 14 April 2023, after having
OL,14,Fsix and a half pints of beer.
OL,16,FHis old school friend Christopher
OL,17,FTromp, who was 20, died at the scene
OL,18,Fof the crash on rural road Cobbs Brow
OL,19,FLane in Newburgh, West Lancashire.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
