OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1774365082
OL,3,CMan who drank six pints before fatal
OL,4,Ccrash that killed friend, jailed
OL,6,FBennett also suffered significant
OL,7,Finjuries and spent several weeks in a
OL,8,Fcoma.
OL,10,FChristopher and Matthew had been for
OL,11,Fdrinks at their hometown in Parbold,
OL,12,Fless than half a mile from
OL,13,FChristopher's home.
OL,15,FThe two are seen on the pub's CCTV
OL,16,Fdrinking in the beer garden at the
OL,17,FWindmill Hotel.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1774365082
OL,3,CMan who drank six pints before fatal
OL,4,Ccrash that killed friend, jailed
OL,6,FBennett, who already had six points on
OL,7,Fhis driving license for speeding, got
OL,8,Finto the car with a bottle of Corona
OL,9,FExtra and drove to McDonald's drive-
OL,10,Fthrough in Skelmersdale whilst under
OL,11,Fthe influence.
OL,13,FBennett was more than likely
OL,14,Ftravelling at 70mph or above in a
OL,15,Fcountryside 40mph zone with no street
OL,16,Flighting.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1774365082
OL,3,CMan who drank six pints before fatal
OL,4,Ccrash that killed friend, jailed
OL,6,FHe lost control of his car at around
OL,7,F10:45pm on a left-hand bend and drove
OL,8,Fon to the wrong side of the road,
OL,9,Fdriving with the driver's side wheel
OL,10,Fon the grass verge before colliding
OL,11,Fwith two sets of trees.
OL,13,FThe force of the collision destroyed
OL,14,Fthe seatbelt mechanisms and
OL,15,FChristopher was thrown from the car.
OL,16,FThe Audi's engine, radiator, front
OL,17,Fgrill and windscreen were also
OL,18,Fejected, with the engine coming to
OL,19,Frest further down the road.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1774365082
OL,3,CMan who drank six pints before fatal
OL,4,Ccrash that killed friend, jailed
OL,6,FChristopher's family said he was an
OL,7,F"incredibly likeable person", who was
OL,8,F"naturally quite academically bright."
OL,10,FChristopher's mum and dad, Julie and
OL,11,FGed said: "When Chris was killed, our
OL,12,Ffamily didn't shatter or break apart,
OL,13,Fwe pulled together and remain close,
OL,14,Fsupporting each other.
OL,16,F"Our lives were shattered of course,
OL,17,Fbut we have tried our utmost to
OL,18,Fmaintain our own dignity and values
OL,19,Fand honour Chris' memory in the very
OL,20,Fbest way we can.
OL,26,@sD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1774365082
OL,3,CMan who drank six pints before fatal
OL,4,Ccrash that killed friend, jailed
OL,6,F"It is not possible to measure the
OL,7,Fimpact of losing him and continuing
OL,8,Fwithout him is incredibly painful. A
OL,9,Fday doesn't go by where we don't think
OL,10,Fabout him and realise, we miss him so
OL,11,Fmuch.
OL,13,FThey added: "We set the dinner table
OL,14,Ffor four not five. We talk about him,
OL,15,Fnot to him. We have lots of photos but
OL,16,Fthere will be no more, and we have to
OL,17,Frely on our memories without the
OL,18,Fopportunity of making new ones.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1774365082
OL,3,CMan who drank six pints before fatal
OL,4,Ccrash that killed friend, jailed
OL,6,F"It is almost three years since Chris
OL,7,Fwas killed, and we have had all that
OL,8,Ftime to try and rebuild some kind of
OL,9,Flife around our grief. However, we
OL,10,Fhave also lived with the knowledge
OL,11,Fthat the person responsible has never
OL,12,Facknowledged this or shown any remorse
OL,13,Ffor his actions."
OL,15,FBennett, formerly of Lawrence Road,
OL,16,FLiverpool, pleaded not guilty to
OL,17,Fcausing death by dangerous driving.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1774365082
OL,3,CMan who drank six pints before fatal
OL,4,Ccrash that killed friend, jailed
OL,6,FAt one point in the trial, Bennett
OL,7,Fattempted to say that he didn't even
OL,8,Fknow if he was the one driving,
OL,9,Fdespite CCTV placing him in the
OL,10,Fdriver's seat.
OL,12,FIt took a jury just 90 minutes to
OL,13,Funanimously find Bennett guilty.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1774365082
OL,3,CMan who drank six pints before fatal
OL,4,Ccrash that killed friend, jailed
OL,6,FHe was sentenced to nine years in
OL,7,Fprison at Preston Crown Court on 24
OL,8,FMarch 2026. He must serve two thirds
OL,9,Fof that sentence before he is eligible
OL,10,Fto be released. He was disqualified
OL,11,Ffrom driving for 11 years and must
OL,12,Fpass an extended re-test before he can
OL,13,Fre-gain his license.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1774365082
OL,3,CMan who drank six pints before fatal
OL,4,Ccrash that killed friend, jailed
OL,6,FSpeaking about the trial, Christopher
OL,7,FTromp's family said: "The four of us
OL,8,Fsat here day after day, holding onto
OL,9,Feach other, watching the video of
OL,10,FChris getting in that car just willing
OL,11,Fhim to turn around and walk home and
OL,12,Fcome back to us. All the while, of
OL,13,Fcourse, knowing he didn't and he isn't.
OL,15,F"Nothing is bringing Chris back to us,
OL,16,Fwe know that but losing him wasn't
OL,17,Fsimply the result of a tragic
OL,18,Faccident, it was avoidable, the result
OL,19,Fof one person's reckless and dangerous
OL,20,Fbehaviour.
OL,26,@oD@VOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1774365082
OL,3,CMan who drank six pints before fatal
OL,4,Ccrash that killed friend, jailed
OL,6,F"Matthew's lack of understanding,
OL,7,Fcompassion and inability to accept
OL,8,Fresponsibility for his actions have
OL,9,Fadded massively to our distress and
OL,10,Fgrief. It has taken a jury to make him
OL,11,Faccept what he has done and that, to
OL,12,Fus, is something incomprehensible."
OL,14,FSergeant Laura Kendall from Lancashire
OL,15,FPolice said: "Christopher was
OL,16,Fevidently a dearly loved young man,
OL,17,Fwho had a long life ahead of him, a
OL,18,Flife that was tragically cut short by
OL,19,FMatthew Bennett's dangerous driving.
OL,26,@tD@cO]wD@NOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39112
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1774365082
OL,3,CMan who drank six pints before fatal
OL,4,Ccrash that killed friend, jailed
OL,6,F"I don't doubt that Bennett never
OL,7,Fintended on taking a life that night,
OL,8,Fbut he did know how much he had to
OL,9,Fdrink, he knew the road ` that it was
OL,10,Fa rural area, surrounded by trees,
OL,11,Fwith a 40mph speed limit - yet he
OL,12,Fstill chose to drive, and to drive
OL,13,Fdangerously.
OL,15,F"He called himself Christopher's
OL,16,Ffriend, yet has not once admitted his
OL,17,Fguilt, forcing Christopher's family
OL,18,Fand loved ones to endure a six day
OL,19,Ftrial.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39113
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1774365082
OL,3,CMan who drank six pints before fatal
OL,4,Ccrash that killed friend, jailed
OL,6,F"It is not my place to comment on the
OL,7,Fsentence passed today, but I do hope
OL,8,Fthat now justice has been done, and
OL,9,FBennett has received a custodial
OL,10,Fsentence, Christopher's family can
OL,11,Ffeel some sense of closure, and that
OL,12,FBennett can reflect on his own actions.
OL,14,F"What happened to Christopher was
OL,15,Fpreventable. Speeding and drink
OL,16,Fdriving is not and never will be ok.
OL,17,FIt is dangerous, it is criminal, and
OL,18,Fit takes lives.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39114
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1774365082
OL,3,CMan who drank six pints before fatal
OL,4,Ccrash that killed friend, jailed
OL,6,F"If you are in the pub or have had a
OL,7,Fdrink and think 'it's ok, I know the
OL,8,Froads', or 'it's ok, I've only had a
OL,9,Ffew', I want you to stop and think of
OL,10,FChristopher.
OL,12,F"I want you to think of his family,
OL,13,Fand what they have said today. You
OL,14,Fcould so easily cause that level of
OL,15,Fdevastation if you choose to get
OL,16,Fbehind the wheel after drinking
OL,17,Falcohol."
OL,26,@nD@AOUyD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/15
